Add user in Im to get the Access key ID and Secret access key - while creatin user, create a group and attach policy "AdministratorAccess"
create a directory
create a .tf file under the directory
terraform init - to initialize the terraform script
terraform validate - to validate whether the code written s correct
terraform apply - to create the instance
terraform destroy - to delete the instance
terrafrom target name - to delete a specific configaration like vpc, s3 bucket etc.

to secure Access key ID and Secret access key, we use AWS-CLI (Command Line Interface)


